
Toy3D is an OpenGL ES toolkit to ease embedded 3D development. Main features include:

  - Wrap OpenGL ES API
  - Provide frequently-used 3D effect control/widget

Toy3D is open source based on GPL.

Toy3D arch is as following:  

-----------------------------------------
|               APP                     |
-----------------------------------------
|             Mobile3D                  |
-----------------------------------------
|            OpenGL ES API              |
-----------------------------------------
|               Kernel                  |
-----------------------------------------
|              Hardware                 |
-----------------------------------------


Mobile3D include: World, Camera, Mesh, Texture, Image.


Mobile3D 0.1
 - Initial version.
 - Core modules include World, Camera, Mesh, Model, Model_am, Image, Texture.
 - Some demos: triangle, rectangle, texture, blending  


